title: Don't Settle For Less
itunes:title: Don't Settle For Less
description:
In seasons of waiting for your promise to come to pass, it’s easy to get discouraged and believe for less than the dream God put in your heart. But if you’re going to become all that God created you to be, you have to refuse to settle for less than what He promised.

Learn more about your ad-choices at https://www.iheartpodcastnetwork.com
